item.title: CVE-2016-9746|2024-08-06T02:59:03.498Z -- ibm -- rational%20team%20concert
item.description: IBM Team Concert (RTC) 4.0, 5.0 and 6.0 is vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 119821.
